<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77eb321c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460vv–19"><num value="460vv–19">§ 460vv–19.</num><heading> Acreages</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The acreage specified in this subchapter is approximate and in the event of discrepancies between cited acreage and the lands depicted on reference maps, the maps shall control.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77eb321d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/499/s21">Pub. L. 100–499, § 21</ref>, <date date="1988-10-18">Oct. 18, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2500">102 Stat. 2500</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
